text: Lovely 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a den nestled in a serene, lightly wooded setting on a quiet dead-end street, just steps away from WWU. This property features an open-concept layout, LVP floors, an eat-in kitchen, and a formal dining room and living room with a cozy fireplace. Enjoy the convenience of nearby trails, parks, schools, Fairhaven, and shopping centers, along with other South Side Bellingham amenities such as local cafes, restaurants, and community events. The backyard provides a peaceful retreat with space for outdoor dining and a garden area. This home offers an excellent opportunity for both owner-occupiers and investors seeking a centrally located rental property.

Beautiful treed lot with 70 ft frontage, on a quiet street and close to the border. Backing onto acreage (that cannot be subdivided) give this prime building lot additional privacy! The homesite area has been cleared for building but there are still some signature mature fir trees for privacy and a forested feel. A two bedroom septic system (Glendon) is already installed and this will save the new owner lots of time and money! Building lots with completed septic systems are a rare find and this location/price ensures exceptional value! Strat building this summer! Power and water available on the street. Quick access to everything Point Roberts has to offer yet tucked away with total privacy.

On the market for the first time, this meticulously maintained custom craftsman home is the perfect blend of Northwest charm & luxurious living. Southern exposure means sunfilled days on the covered patio on Semiahmoo's 13th fairway. Thoughtfully designed 3, 109 sqft floor plan offers main floor living & an open yet defined kitchen/dining/living space. Vaulted ceilings, excellent craftsmanship, chef's kitchen, top-of-the-line appliances. Designed by an engineer this custom home features a well-thought-out dual-fuel 3-zone heating & cooling system. The attention to detail is without comparison. Not to disappoint the primary has a fireplace & spa bath. Are you looking for an exceptional home? If you're a discerning buyer, your search is over.

This beautiful, fully remodeled home sits on 5 private acres & features 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms & a spacious office that could easily function as a main level bedroom. In addition to the interior remodel, the home boasts a recently replaced roof, Air-Conditioning, a brand-new water filtration system, updated septic & a newly fenced area for your furry friends. The large deck and patio provide the perfect outdoor space to entertain your guests while being surrounded by nature. The oversized 2-car garage also includes a separate heated living area, ideal for an ADU or MIL conversion. There is also an additional outbuilding with heat & powerperfect for a little office outside the home. As an added bonus, it's only 10 minutes from Bellingham!

Charming, well-maintained home on a private corner lot w/easy access to new medical facilities, schools, parks and everything Lynden has to offer. Home features 3 beds, 2 full baths, generous and open living/dining area, vaulted ceilings, cozy gas fireplace and large windows to bring in natural light. Enjoy your fireplace on the cold NW days and A/C in the summer. Kitchen includes an eat in breakfast area w/walk-in pantry and plenty of counter and cabinet space! Primary bedroom has a large walk-in closet, double vanity and private bathroom area. Beautifully landscaped back yard offers privacy, 2 patio areas, large storage shed and raised garden beds. Plenty of parking with a 2 car garage and large driveway with room for an RV or trailer.

Edgemoor! Completely remodeled {NW Energy Certified} Passive Solar one-level home in Bellinghams highly sought-after Southside. Designed for ease of living. Endless natural light with an open floor plan and walls of windows. Rebuilt with eco-friendly features. Culinary kitchen designed for entertaining. Pulldown ladder to deluxe insulated attic storage. Spacious deck with fully-fenced backyard and garden space. 1-car garage with epoxy floors, storage and EV charging station. Metal roof with Solar. Quiet neighborhood. Easy bike or stroll to downtown Fairhaven, Marine Park, Ferry Terminal, and Waterfront. Interurban Trail and dog park just steps from your back gate. It doesn't get any better than this location and a fabulous home.

This Charming Craftsman Bungalow in the Columbia neighborhood awaits! This 2 bedroom, 1 bath home has been tastefully updated throughout and is move in ready. A large backyard and deck offer the perfect setting for outdoor gatherings and gardening adventures. And who doesn't appreciate some extra storage space in the garage? Basement also offers additional storage or could be workout area or? The perfect blend of cozy and functional living. Close to shopping, restaurants and is in a wonderful neighborhood for evening strolls.

Welcoming Craftsman retreat in the historic York Neighborhood! Perfect for first-time home buyers or astute investors, this delightful abode features not just one, but 2 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms. Step into a sun-drenched haven w/a yard bathed in all-day sunshine, complemented by a Trex wrap-around deckan entertainer's dream! Inside, bask in the glow of natural light that floods the interiors, accentuating the timeless fir floors in the living room. With ample off-street parking, convenience is at your doorstep. Steps from Nelson's Market, parks, downtown, & the I5, this home offers the perfect blend of tranquility & accessibility. Roof rebuilt in 2020. Great opportunity to own a piece of history in one of the most sought-after neighborhoods.

Custom single level home located on a fully fenced 17, 424 sqft lot ideal for pets, gardening and/or weekend gatherings. Home offers a private rural setting while being conveniently located to Lake Padden recreation park, shopping, retail or I-5 access. Beautifully designed home offers an open floor plan, generous window package, large rooms, tall ceilings, flowing layout, hardwood and cork floors throughout. Light & bright oversized kitchen, granite tile counter tops, beautiful wood cabinets, dining eating area, plus semi formal dining room, (or office). Stone entry, large foyer, w/ French-doors leading to a large family room, a deluxe fireplace and bookshelf design, Den could be used as 4 bedrooms.

Quiet top-floor end unit pristine condo in a prime location in South Bellingham. This 2-bedroom condo at Willowwood is ideally located across the street from the trails of Sehome Hill Arboretum and a short distance to shopping and restaurants at Sehome Village and Western Washington University. The living area is open and bright with a cozy fireplace and the bedrooms are spacious. Soak in the views from the peaceful covered balcony overlooking evergreen trees for extra privacy and tranquility. One assigned parking space and parking for guests. The condo complex is well-maintained with a newer roof, windows, exterior paint and newly resurfaced parking lot. Great investment or home close to Fairhaven, outdoor adventures and endless amenities.

Discover a home that offers endless adventures just outside your doorstep and be surrounded by nature. Move in ready 3 bdrm 1 3/4 bath home w/ freshly painted interior, new base & door trim, door hardware, lower-level carpet, & almost all new light fixtures. The home features an inviting spacious great room w/ fireplace, vaulted ceilings, skylights, & an abundance of natural light. Level entry from the garage to the lower-level w/ 1 bdrm, bath, and family room. New exterior paint, refreshed landscaping, & composite front and back decks. Situated in Sudden Valley w/ hiking, golfing, clubhouse, restaurant, beaches, outdoor pools, parks, marina, ball fields, disc golf, boat launch, tennis and basketball courts, and more.

Welcome to the beautiful Community of Sudden Valley! This is a perfect starter home! Relax on your back deck in a quiet wooded setting. The bright open kitchen with vaulted ceilings has a cozy eating nook. New laminate floors extend throughout the living, dining and bedrooms. Nothing better than a nice fire in the wood stove that heats the whole house. Main living includes a bedroom, full bath and laundry. Awesome spacious primary has a full bath and huge walk-in closet. Downstairs features an extra room that could be used as a bedroom, rec room or office. New roof installed late last year. Enjoy all SV amenities - golf course, swimming pool, tennis courts, walking trails, boat launch.

This quality built Northwest Contemporary home in the Hannah Creek neighborhood sits at the gateway to Galbraith Mountain with miles of trails accessible right from your doorstep. As you enter this elegant home, the stellar views of Bellingham Bay and the Canadian Coastal Range greet you through the picture windows in the light and bright great room. The well-thought out floor plan takes advantage of the views from much of the home including the primary suite with its own sliding glass door and deck. The single level floor plan includes two wings: the primary suite in one, and two bedrooms plus a full bath in the other. Whatcom Falls Park and the urban trail system are just a short walk or bike ride away.

Welcome to 7392 Clamdigger Dr, Blaine, WA, the perfect home for those looking for a blend of comfort and practicality. This inviting corner lot home features a unique third hobby garage, ideal for storage or creative projects. Fresh exterior paint gives the house a bright, welcoming feel. Inside, the spacious primary bedroom offers a comfortable retreat, while two cozy living spaces provide plenty of room for relaxation and entertainment. Imagine the peace of mind that comes with owning this home where it not only provides a comfortable living space but also acts as a safety net for your future. This property offers a solid investment opportunity, allowing you to build equity and financial security over time.

Live the dream on the shores of Lake Samish!! First time on the market since 1966 is this sun drenched lake view home ready for its next chapter. Large living room, kitchen, full bath and bedroom on the main floor with oversized windows and a walk out to the deck. Upstairs are two more lakeview bedrooms, a full bath and bonus craft room that could be converted to a 4th bedroom. Both bedrooms have sliders leading to the upstairs deck. Enjoy the lake lifestyle on the big deck, yard and bulkhead. Then go out the private dock to fish, swim or boat. This is on a small lane off E. Lk. Samish rd shared by only 5 homes. Last lot is a rarely used rec. lot. Plenty of off street parking and many outbuildings for toys. Fast 10 minute drive to Fairhaven

Unwind at this tranquil creekside sanctuary, nestled beyond a hedgerow at the end of a private drive. Enjoy the convenience of in-town living near schools, Bender Plaza amenities, and Bender Fields. This custom built well-maintained home features an open layout, air conditioning, cozy wood-burning stone fireplace, main floor primary suite with spacious walk-thru closet & private patio, flex room/office, loft, reading nook, and bonus room. The chef's kitchen boasts Sub-Zero & Wolf appliances. Gather around the firepit, explore Fishtrap Creek, pick berries, nurture the garden, daydream in the hammock on the bank of the babbling creek. This is the ideal setting for entertaining or quiet relaxation.

Nestled in a vibrant 55+ community, this charming 2-bedroom, 1.75-bath home offers a blend of comfort and convenience. Lots of light throughout. Complete with modern amenities like air conditioning to keep you cool on warm summer days and a cornered gas fireplace for cold winter nights. With access to a clubhouse, you'll have endless opportunities to socialize, stay active, and make lasting memories with neighbors and friends. For investors seeking a promising opportunity, this property comes with a reliable tenant in place until June 30, 2025, providing immediate rental income potential. Don't miss your chance to invest in this sought-after community.

Step into the future of stylish living w/this chic, updated home designed for todays buyers. The layout features a main-level bedroom. Embrace the luxury plank vinyl floors and custom window treatments that perfectly complement your urban aesthetic. Enjoy sunset views from the 2nd story balcony and access to Birch Bay waterfront trails and restaurants, a gated community that speaks to your active lifestyle. Kick back on the covered front porch, shoot some hoops or host gatherings on the back patio. Enjoy the drop zone mudroom off the garage, and swoon over the modernized bthrms and kitchen with a masculine edge and detail. Seize the opportunity to own this uniquely stylish home that captures the essence of living w/ flair and finesse.

Enjoy endless bay views of Dot Island, Bellingham Bay, & the San Juans accented by breathtaking sunsets from iconic Chuckanut mountain. Unwind on a large, covered deck, providing the perfect backdrop for the Pacific Northwest! Enter a great room flooded with natural light from massive West facing windows & towering vaulted ceilings open to a lofted second floor. Features include a primary bedroom with ensuite on main floor, chef's kitchen leading to an outdoor covered dining area & views from almost every room. Out your front door step onto the beautiful Interurban trail with access to Larabee State Park & limitless opportunities to explore & enjoy the great outdoors. Live a life of coastal beauty, while only minutes from Fairhaven Village.

Welcome to River-Walk, a unique NW Washington community offering attractive design, luxurious finishes, beautiful views & pedestrian-friendly connectivity to Lynden. Walk or bike a few blocks to downtown to Lyndens quaint restaurants & stores. River-Walk is less than two hours to Seattle, Vancouver, B.C., Mt. Baker & the San Juan Islands. Lot 7 is in River-Walks west side, reserved for 55-and-older active adults with tech features including high-speed fiber optic cable. It offers a comfortable 2, 013 sqft with 3 bedrooms & 2.25 bathrooms. The gourmet kitchen is highlighted by quartz countertops & islands with full waterfall drops. Direct GPS to 202 Riverview Road, Lynden.

A beautifully forested 20+ acres featuring 100+ ft creek frontage and plentiful sites perfect for camping or recreation. Enjoy seclusion with easy access to amenities! This property is located less than 10 minutes from Blue Mountain Grill, Acme Diner & about 30 minutes to the center of Bellingham. Currently in Forestry and Buyer to continue in Forestry or pay to remove it (Est $14-15K by Assessor). Buyer to verify availability of utilities. Shown by appointment only.

Opportunity knocks on this nearly 19.27 acre vacant land piece on H Street Road! Zoned Residential, bring your creative ideas and develop this property into your dream estate! Blaine is a gem nestled between Seattle, WA and Vancouver, BC and located just minutes to an international airport, two US/CAN border crossings, I-5 access + two saltwater marinas. Lynden School District.

Located in Bellingham's sought after Edgemoor neighborhood, sits this charming turn-key home with tasteful updates throughout! A spacious kitchen and living area overlook the large, level, fully fenced backyard, all adjacent to your separately accessed cozy guest suite that offers a lot of potential uses. If you love hiking, biking, or taking a nature walk, the interurban & Chuckanut Mountain trail system is just blocks away, or you can stroll through close-by Historic Fairhaven, and its waterfront, deciding which restaurant or brewery you're eating at tonight. Whether winding down after an outdoor shower in the dry sauna, or the hot tub with its distant water views, this home is the perfect place to relax after your adv

Escape to your private park-like retreat minutes from I-5 in beautiful Lake Samish Neighborhood. Charming 4-bedroom craftsman home offers modern convenience on over 1 acre, w/ territorial views & view of Lookout Mountain. Features include; vaulted ceilings, natural fir accents, wood stove & abundant light. Recent upgrades include; new heat pump/AC, remodeled 3/4 bath, & premium maintenance-free gutters. Private well has a newer whole-house filtration system, water gardens w/ eco-friendly rain catchment. The property also offers a fire pit, hot tub, ample parking (including room for a boat or RV), carport, detached garage w/separate living space above, complete w/ 3/4 bath and kitchenette. Enjoy the amenities of the Lake Samish Neighborhood.

Large lot in Everson with room for a shop. This lot features over 17, 000 sq ft. out of the flood zone and all services are in. Located on a private paved road with ample space for your dream home. Call today!

First time ever on the market! Solid 1929 home on 5.95 acres with pasture, fruit trees and peaceful setting. Stucco exterior, new roof in 2024, vinyl plank flooring in kitchen, fir floors in the bedrooms, oak flooring in the living room under carpet, double pane windows. Baseboard heat + gas fireplace. Some updated electrical and paint. 20 minutes to downtown Bellingham. Elderly owners have moved to assisted living and the house is vacant, waiting for new owners to love & care for it.

Welcome to 1520 Lowell Ave! Nestled on a large parklike lot, this 3BD/1.75BA single level home is perfectly located close to everything, but far enough to give it that secluded, private feel. Close to I-5, shopping, Lake Whatcom, World Class Galbraith Mountain, groceries, Whatcom Falls Park, trails, & so much more. Hard to beat this location! Hardwood floors & newer laminate throughout. New metal roof(home and carport) in 2019, recent interior & exterior paint. French doors off the primary bedroom, fully fenced back yard, detached garage/carport & tons of exterior storage! Set back off the road w/long driveway giving a super private & quiet feel. The recently added skylight lets in so much natural light!Mature landscaping & two large decks!

Welcome to luxury single-story living in Lynden! This 2, 621 sqft 2 car garage home boasts two full suites, each with walk-in closets and 3/4 bathrooms alongside a third bathroom and an office for added convenience. Entertain effortlessly in the open living space complete with spacious kitchen, dining area and carpeted living room leading to a covered back porch. For more formal occasions, the separate dining room, connected to the kitchen via a butler's pantry offers an elegant setting for gatherings. Outside the yard and shed provide additional space for outdoor activities and storage. With a dedicated laundry room and ample storage throughout this home combines style and functionality seamlessly, all conveniently close to town and NO HOA

Introducing this magnificent custom home located in The Woodlands of Edgemoor. Featuring chefs kitchen with professional grade appliances, butlers pantry, 2 garages (one on each level) and custom millwork throughout. Main level living makes this home ideal for hosting guests on their own floor! Experience the unique and thoughtfully designed landscaping, inviting covered deck with fireplace, dining area and man made creek. This home is a short way to Historic Fairhaven, Magical Trails, and Bellingham Bay. The primary suite features its own deck, spacious bathroom and absolutely stunning walk-in closet. No expense was spared in the execution of this beautiful estate. This home has been maintained with the utmost level of care.

Nearly new & well cared for home on a corner lot in Pacific Highlands. Bright, open floor plan with mid-day westerly exposure offering stunning sunsets. The main floor has high ceilings, a gas fireplace & an office/4th bedroom. Elegant finishes including quartz countertops throughout the home. Enjoy a chef's kitchen with stainless steel appliances which is open to the dining area with easy patio access. Main floor laundry, on-demand hot water & a hot tub in the fully fenced back yard. Upstairs you'll find the oversized primary suite with a huge walk-in closet & upscale bathroom. Two more bedrooms & a full bath upstairs as well. This is a beautiful, truly move-in ready home! Community features include playgrounds & tennis courts.

The one you've been waiting for, a gorgeous classic craftsman in the idyllic Cornwall Park neighborhood. You'll be welcomed by an open dining area bathed in sunlight, ft cherry hardwood floors that seamlessly flow into the living room w/views of the backyard. Updated kitchen fts plenty of counter space, newer SS appliances & mudroom leading onto the deck. Main level full bath has a soaker tub & walk-in shower. Upstairs fts a half bath & 3 BRs & updated windows throughout. Backyard is an oasis complete w/sauna, new patio extension, new fence, garden beds, mature fruit trees & a detached garage w/ automatic door + workbench. The perfect location: close to breweries, parks, shopping, the waterfront & brimming with ADU potential.

Your perfect waterfront home awaits! Large, west facing windows allow natural light to absorb the space. Home features 20ft high ceilings. With luxury touches throughout and modern design, this home is complete with an open living room kitchen area featuring quartz countertops, high end appliances, island, plenty of cabinetry all on polished concrete flooring on the main level. Step outside to your concrete patio perfect for lounging or entertaining. As you head upstairs on your led lit stairway, you can take in the picturesque, ocean front views. Large primary allows for unlimited sunsets.Access to your beach just steps away. 3rd room can be used as extra bedroom/office or den. Fee Simple (you own land and structure).
nearby_schools: Lummi High School, Ferndale School District, Lummi Elementary School

text: A townhome that lives like a standalone w/ the benefits that an HOA provides; lawn maintenance, exterior repair, etc. Featuring the primary bedroom on the main floor + 2 more bedrooms and a loft upstairs! This home has been tastefully updated w/ modern high-end cabinets, backsplash, faucets, stainless appliances, AC & more! The living room has a gas fireplace, built-in cabinets & 20+ ft ceilings, letting in all the light you could ask for + Mt Baker views! The primary suite has its own gas fireplace, walk-in closet, built-in closet & en suite w/ soaker tub & tile walk-in shower. Two add'tl rooms upstairs are oversized with deep walk-in closets. The loft space could be an office, playroom, etc. Walk to restaurants, coffee, and Bender fields!

A great investment opportunity with major expandability possibilities! 8% Cap Rate! Zoned Urban Residential gives you tons of versatility on highest and best use. Included with the sale is the adjacent lot that is 5, 663 sqft. Boasting 7 units in total - five of them are beautiful, fully renovated units, 6th unit just needs some finishing touches. Renovate the store front for even more income. Huge laundry area with coin-op machines and storage units. Use 2 car garage for yourself or rent that too! Tenants will love living right across from Griffintown Park. Walking distance to downtown Ferndale shops, restaurants and Vanderyacht, Pioneer and Hovander Homestead parks!

Nestled along the shoreline this exquisite 3bed, 3.5bath home offers luxurious living at its finest. Inside a spacious & inviting interior, is adorned w/ elegant finishes & flooded w/ natural light. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects living, dining & kitchen areas perfect for entertaining. Prepare to be captivated by breathtaking views from the expansive deck & soak in the beauty all around you! The primary boasts panoramic windows framing picturesque ocean views, ensuite & ample closet space. For the hobbyist or car enthusiast, the large garage provides plenty of space for vehicles & an extra workshop for tinkering. Located minutes from local amenities, dining & outdoor recreation, this home offers luxury, comfort & convenience.

South facing building lot in South Beach area with beach rights! Property is on Orcas Way, a dead-end road and a short walk to the beach. Recent soils test confirms Glendon Biofilter is possible. Lot has been cleared in the past. Come enjoy the peace and tranquility of Point Roberts!

Step into luxury living inside this immaculate better-than-new single-story 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home. The kitchen is a chef's dream with ample cabinets, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and a generous bar eating area, seamlessly connecting to the dinning room. Retreat to spacious bedrooms for ultimate relaxation. Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the entire home, adding to its allure and durability. Stay cool and comfortable with the mini-split AC system. Enjoy the convenience of an insulated garage. Take in breathtaking mountain views from the comfort of your home in this exclusive gated community. Experience the epitome of modern living in this exceptional home just 30 minutes to Bellingham!

Nestled near Lake Terrell \\ This private 2 acre Home Features 3 Beds 2 Bath. Open, Sunny floor plan + Outbuilding that includes extra covered parking and tons of storage. Detached Shop + Work area \\ Flat level lot \\ sunroom \\ Multiple mature fruit trees. Mins to town, shopping & I5.

Welcome to this wonderful oasis in the sudden valley community. This hidden gem with lots to offer on a wonder flat lot with easy access into the home. Walking in you will instantly notice the open feel with the vaulted ceilings and natural light that floods in. You will notice the pristine condition of the new decks, new roof, new mini splits with A/C and a new retaining wall in the driveway. There is a large bedroom on the main floor and an upstairs loft with a bedroom. The daylight basement offers an outside entrance with wonderful potential to have a full ADU, add another bathroom or use it as a large third bedroom, There are many possibilities to be had. Come tour and welcome to your MOVE IN READY home.

Welcome home to this beautifully updated 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom residence. Step inside to discover bright laminate flooring throughout most of the home, complemented by brand new carpet in two of the bedrooms. The house boasts a new roof installed in 2022, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. Outside, a spacious deck awaits, complete with a luxurious hot tub for relaxing evenings under the stars. Additionally, the front yard features a charming vegetable garden, along with a large outbuilding for all your outdoor supplies. RV enthusiasts will appreciate the RV parking with the convenient plug-in. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home.

B6 Premier 40 foot slip and location, 2 ft overhangs allowed. ! You can't get much closer to the main dock. Semiahmoo Marina! History, majesty, mystery...what a great place to moor your boat! Semiahmoo's historic water tower stands sentinel. To the East, majestic Mt. Baker...and mystery, why are all those cars cruising Marine Drive in White Rock?! Semiahmoo Marina is only 16 nautical miles from the legendary, mystical San Juan Islands. Canada's Gulf Islands and the Inside Passage are favorite nearby destinations. Golf, tennis and swimming are available for a fee @ Semiahmoo Golf & County Club. Nice facilities, store, laundry and more. 2 hours from Seattle, 36 miles to Vancouver BC. Canada.

Great investment opportunity knocks.This 3 bed 2 bath house in the Roosevelt neighborhood is currently being used as a rental but would also make a great first time buyers' home as well. This lovely home features a huge backyard with fruit trees. This house boasts a 68 walk-ability score and is just a short distance to the railroad trail and barkley village and all that it has to offer. It is also close to roosevelt elementary, roosevelt park, and the boys and girls club.

Incredible turn-key opportunity on the edge of downtown Ferndale. New construction zero lot line townhome with 2 beds 1.5 baths, 2 decks & deep (nearly 2 car) garage. Space for a car, plus workshop/storage in the back. Highly efficient units feature heat pumps w/AC. Private washer/dryer. Building improvements have an 8-year tax exemption, so you only pay taxes on the land! Walking distance to parks, schools, downtown & close to I-5 access. Owner-occupant loans are available with zero down & investment loans are available with as little as 5% down. Excellent to live in OR rent as a high income & low maintenance investment! Seller will credit $5, 000 towards buyers closing costs.

Very large corner lot with a beautiful 2012 Fleetwood Park Model. This unit is turnkey and ready to enjoy all of the amenities of The Glen. With a covered 320 sq. ft. deck and a well-insulated 154 sq. ft. gazebo, and plenty of parking for a guest RV, this is a property to grab up. Property has a nice shed, heated water supply line for the winter months, and so much more. Located close to Mt. Baker, this is a perfect place to stay in the winter for skiing, or in the summer for hiking. The Glen has 24/7 Security w/gated entrance, 2 pools, hot tub, 2 clubhouses, sauna, playgrounds, river access, laundry facilities, restrooms w/ showers, library, disc golf course, pump track, trails, and so much more! Zoned rec. for 120 days use/yr.

Amazing New construction home, started and with a finish date of June 2024. Bay view from the upper front deck will be amazing. 2 Primary bedroom with 1 upstairs with walk in shower & tub, walk in closet, private deck with view of the water, Primary bedroom on the main floor with walk in closet, luxury bathroom with walk in tiled shower, Huge office & Huge Bonus room over the garage. Open to below living room with floor to ceiling stone wrapped fireplace. Elegant modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances included, Quartz counter tops, soft close cabinets, large breakfast bar and private view out your back deck to your back yard with trees and shade. This development has private access to the beach and community area.

Age in place in this main floor living design, blessed with an abundance of light, a large patio deck, & a bonus suite for your in-laws or extra income. You will love this home with its vaulted cedar ceiling, 2 gas fireplaces, cozy sunken living room, large windows, main flr primary suite, & two brand-new showers. The extra large lot will delight with it patio, garden spaces, and fully fenced yard. The basement offers additional space for bedroom(s) and the nicely apportioned mother-in-law suite is complete with private bath and laundry hookups. There is plenty to appreciate from the round-about driveway, two car garage, and garden shed, and the home's proximity to area schools and downtown. $5000 flooring credit offered by seller.

Parting is such sweet sorrow, however, after 37 years of ownership of this lovingly maintained home in the county, this is an opportunity for living in this beautiful home, and making it yours. Just shy of an acre, with picturesque scenery and an abundance of wild life, plus the incredible sunsets, will await. With 3 beds, 2 full baths, a hidey room off the primary behind the closet can be a study, zoom or hobby room. There's an enclosed family room/den, or home office. In addition to a 2 car attached garage, there's a separate storage building, large patio, and ample room for a boat, or a collectable car. Make this space a hobby farm and add some chickens and a garden. There's room for everyone. This is a sweet spot.

A classic NW contemporary rambler in an idyllic natural setting on 5 private acres includes it all for modern country living w/ the convenience of being just 10 mins to town. A gorgeous chef's kitchen embodies the heart of this home w/ high-end Thermador fridge, butler pantry & cast iron wood stove. 3 generously sized bedrooms, remodeled primary suite & laundry all on the main. Extensive recent improvements ensure the home is structurally sound & well maintained for many years to come w/ new deck, hardie siding, trim, perimeter drainage & encapsulated crawl space. Heated shop on lower level w/ exterior access, rubber flooring & stainless workbench. Garage equipped w/ 50 amp, 220 plug 60 amp circuits & wired for generator. Pre-inspected.

WOW, the crown jewel of Paradise Lakes is now available! Sellers custom built home shows pride in design & finishes throughout.Immediately captivated by the grand soaring entrance, and smooth flowing floor plan, you are engulfed in all the attention to detail featuring high coffered ceilings w/ recessed lighting, crown molding & detailed millwork, hardwood floors, custom tile work, grand wood fireplace, granite counters, SS appliances, custom cabinetry, lighting & fixtures, in-wall speakers, & more. Four spacious bedrooms upstairs including the majestic primary w/ en-suite bathroom.No expense spared for comfort w/ tankless hot water, heat pump & AC. Spacious covered back deck perfect for entertaining on a bright sunny quiet cul-de-sac lot.

Affordable home ownership! Stop paying rent! Nice 2-bedroom Cottage Creek condo looks out onto a green area. Pets allowed! Central location is close to many amenities including bus line and Whatcom Community College. 2 bedrooms and 1.5 baths. Washer & dryer in the condo! Exterior has been recently updated with new siding, paint, & roof. One assigned parking space right in front of condo, plus ample visitor spots. Private deck with storage closet also looks out on to green area. Cozy wood-burning fireplace for winter evenings! Stainless appliances in well laid out kitchen! Dues cover water, sewer, garbage, and exterior maintenance. Condo Association is professionally managed. 48-hour notice needed for showings.

Experience one-level living in the charming town of Lynden! This lovely home boasts a back yard oasis, perfect for entertaining, with a covered patio and fully fenced yard. Additionally, it features an irrigation system for easy maintenance. Recent upgrades include new carpet and paint. The home offers a great floor plan, including a spacious primary suite with a bathroom and generous closet space. Conveniently located near Lynden's amenities, you'll enjoy easy access to local parks, shops, restaurants, and more.

Let the covered porch welcome you to this beautiful and meticulously maintained rambler in Blaine, Washington! This delightful 3 bed/2 bath home proudly boasts brand new exterior paint (2024), newer roof (2020), and water heater (2021). Single level living at its finest with an ensuite primary bath and a fully fenced backyard that backs up to a serene greenbelt with trails, perfect for relaxing mornings or evenings on the patio. Minutes to amenities, Birch Bay State Park, waterfront restaurants, and the famous C-Shop. Enjoy easy access to Bellingham, Ferndale, and Lynden, with the Canadian border only a short drive away. This home combines ultimate comfort and a prime location for an ideal living experience. Don't miss your opportunity!

Comfortable and clean move in ready three-bedroom two bath 1500 SQ. FT. home, large kitchen with casual dining area, living room, family room. Forced air heat and propane airtight.
